  .how-it-works--container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      text-align: center;
  }
  .how-it-works--container h2 {
      color: #feca57;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px black;
  }
  .how-it-works .section {
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border: 3px dashed #feca57;
  }
  .how-it-works .section h3 {
      color: #ff9f43;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px black;
  }
  .how-it-works .section p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .how-it-works .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1dd1a1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .how-it-works .neon-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #ff9f43;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: black;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 6px white;
      transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .how-it-works .neon-button:hover {
      background: #ee5253;
      transform: scale(1.1);
  }
</style>


<div class="how-it-works--container">
  <h2>🎨 Create Your Custom Tattoo Shoes 👟</h2>
  
  <div class="how-it-works section">
      <h3>🛒 Explore & Shop</h3>
      <p><span class="highlight">All Shoes</span> are Tattoo My Shoes Brand unless you select a different option.</p>
      <p>Need inspiration? Click <a href="#" class="neon-button">Shop All Shoes</a> to browse unique designs.</p>
      <p>Check out our <span class="highlight">gallery</span> and videos for a closer look at our custom kicks.</p>
      <p>Snag a <span class="highlight">Ready-to-Ship</span> pair instantly—no wait time!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="how-it-works section">
      <h3>🎭 Design Your Own Custom Kicks</h3>
      <p>Want something truly one-of-a-kind? Got a favorite artist?</p>
      <p>Click their name or picture to see their 🔥 exclusive designs.</p>
      <p>Pick your <span class="highlight">size, quantity</span>, and add to cart. Boom—your custom journey begins!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="how-it-works section">
      <h3>✍️ Hand-Drawn Tattoo Shoes</h3>
      <p>Want authentic, hand-drawn art? Select <span class="highlight">Ernie Moreno (ME)</span> for exclusive designs.</p>
      <p>Need to chat first? Hit up our <span class="highlight">Live Chat</span>—I usually reply fast! ⚡</p>
      <p>Describe your dream design, choose an <span class="highlight">art style</span>, and let’s bring it to life! 💥</p>
      <p>Prices start at <span class="highlight">$150</span>, depending on design complexity.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="how-it-works section">
      <h3>🖨️ Custom Printed Shoes</h3>
      <p><span class="highlight">Talk to Us Before Ordering!</span></p>
      <p>Send your design or photos to <span class="highlight">tattoomyshoes@gmail.com</span> 🎨📩</p>
      <p>We’ll create a digital preview—once approved, place your order and let’s make magic happen! 👟🔥</p>
      <p>Pick your <span class="highlight">size, shoe style (low/high tops), and quantity</span>, then check out.</p>
  </div>
</div>


